{
  "page": "Smiler",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Botley\" title=\"House Botley\"><img alt=\"House Botley.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/ca/House_Botley.svg/50px-House_Botley.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ca/House_Botley.svg/75px-House_Botley.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ca/House_Botley.svg/100px-House_Botley.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Smiler</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\"><img alt=\"House Greyjoy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/50px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/75px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/100px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Fishman_Smiler.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Marc Fishman Smiler.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/Marc_Fishman_Smiler.jpg/350px-Marc_Fishman_Smiler.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"/images/c/c9/Marc_Fishman_Smiler.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Smiler is burned, by Marc Fishman</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Owners</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Sawane_Botley\" title=\"Sawane Botley\">Sawane Botley</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Species</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">Horse</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\nIn&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a>,&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Smiler</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">warhorse</a> purchased by <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Lordsport\" title=\"Lordsport\">Lordsport</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smiler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Smiler_(horse)\" title=\"Category:Images of Smiler (horse)\">Images of Smiler</a></div>\n<p>Smiler is a stallion, smaller than a destrier, but larger than a courser. He is black, and has a black temper to match. Smiler has \"fire in his eyes\", and has been described as a \"hellhorse\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smiler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smiler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:A_homecoming_not_quite_as_expected_by_thrumugnyr.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/74/A_homecoming_not_quite_as_expected_by_thrumugnyr.jpg/350px-A_homecoming_not_quite_as_expected_by_thrumugnyr.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"176\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/74/A_homecoming_not_quite_as_expected_by_thrumugnyr.jpg/525px-A_homecoming_not_quite_as_expected_by_thrumugnyr.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/74/A_homecoming_not_quite_as_expected_by_thrumugnyr.jpg/700px-A_homecoming_not_quite_as_expected_by_thrumugnyr.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:A_homecoming_not_quite_as_expected_by_thrumugnyr.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> returns home angrily with Smiler and his squire, <a href=\"/index.php/Wex_Pyke\" title=\"Wex Pyke\">Wex Pyke</a>. Art by Thrumugnyr ©</div></div></div>\n<p>A year before, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Sawane_Botley\" title=\"Sawane Botley\">Sawane Botley</a> had bought the black stallion in <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a>, but he proved to be too much horse for him. Theon Greyjoy, who wishes to find a quality horse to ride in battle, is pleased to find Lord Botley's horse on the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>, where good horses are rare. Part of Lord Botley's price for the horse is that Theon must take his <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> nephew, <a href=\"/index.php/Wex_Pyke\" title=\"Wex Pyke\">Wex Pyke</a>, as his <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a>. The horse's size suits Theon, as does his temper. When the stallion first meets his new owner, he tries to bite his face off. Theon names the horse \"Smiler\" because someone Theon once knew said he smiled at all the wrong things.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/Lordsport\" title=\"Lordsport\">Lordsport</a>, Theon meets a woman calling herself Esgred, who Theon can tell is impressed with Smiler. He rides double with her to <a href=\"/index.php/Pyke\" title=\"Pyke\">Pyke</a>, flirting while Esgred asks him questions about his life and family. Theon is shocked when Esgred is revealed as his sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>Theon brings Smiler to <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> with him when he <a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Capture of Winterfell\">captures it</a>. He rides Smiler while hunting his escaped <a href=\"/index.php/Hostage\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hostage\">hostages</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Rickon_Stark\" title=\"Rickon Stark\">Rickon Stark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>  Theon also rides Smiler when parleying with <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a> outside the gates of Winterfell. When <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Luwin\" title=\"Luwin\">Luwin</a> advises Theon to <a href=\"/index.php/Take_the_black\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Take the black\">take the black</a>, Theon considers it, thinking that he has plenty of black clothing, and even his horse is black.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">sack of Winterfell</a>, Theon briefly recovers consciousness after his cheekbone is shattered by <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Snow</a>, and the last thing he sees is Smiler, kicking free of the burning stables with his mane on fire, screaming and rearing.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> After Bran and Rickon and their companions emerge from where they were hiding in the <a href=\"/index.php/Crypts_of_Winterfell\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Crypts of Winterfell\">crypts of Winterfell</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Osha\" title=\"Osha\">Osha</a> points out to Bran the arrows in Theon's fallen warhorse.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smiler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Theon, who has been <a href=\"/index.php/Torture\" title=\"Torture\">tortured</a> by Ramsay for months, is sent by him to <a href=\"/index.php/Moat_Cailin\" title=\"Moat Cailin\">Moat Cailin</a> to end <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Moat_Cailin\" title=\"Siege of Moat Cailin\">its siege</a>. Before giving the <a href=\"/index.php/Gift_of_mercy\" title=\"Gift of mercy\">gift of mercy</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Ralf_Kenning\" title=\"Ralf Kenning\">Ralf Kenning</a>, Theon remembers he once had a horse. He remembers that Smiler's screams had sounded almost human; that with his mane afire, he had reared up on his hind legs, blind with pain, lashing out with his hooves. However, Theon rejects the memory, denying that <a href=\"/index.php/Reek#A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"Reek\">Reek</a> ever had a horse, and slits Ralf's throat.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Much later, in <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>'s yard, Theon remembers the day that Ramsay had set his horse afire, recalling again the manner of Smiler's death, and noting that the horse burning was the last sight he had seen on the day the castle fell.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smiler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Theon_and_Esgred_by_Mike_S_Miller.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/Theon_and_Esgred_by_Mike_S_Miller.jpg/350px-Theon_and_Esgred_by_Mike_S_Miller.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"525\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/Theon_and_Esgred_by_Mike_S_Miller.jpg/525px-Theon_and_Esgred_by_Mike_S_Miller.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/Theon_and_Esgred_by_Mike_S_Miller.jpg/700px-Theon_and_Esgred_by_Mike_S_Miller.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Theon_and_Esgred_by_Mike_S_Miller.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> leaves <a href=\"/index.php/Lordsport\" title=\"Lordsport\">Lordsport</a>, riding with \"<a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Esgred</a>\" on his horse Smiler. Cover of <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings_(comics)\" title=\"A Clash of Kings (comics)\">A Clash of Kings: The Graphic Novel</a>, vol.1 issue #13, by Mike S. Miller.</div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Where did you find that hellhorse?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">\"Esgred\"</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The last thing Theon Greyjoy saw was Smiler, kicking free of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">burning stables</a> with his mane ablaze, screaming, rearing...<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Theon:</b> Kill <a href=\"/index.php/Ralf_Kenning\" title=\"Ralf Kenning\">him</a>. His wits are gone. He's full of blood and worms.<br />\n</p><p><b>Guard:</b> <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">The captain</a> put him in command.<br />\n<b>Theon:</b> You'd put a dying <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">horse</a> down.<br />\n<b>Guard:</b> What horse? I never had no horse.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Theon (thinking):</b> <i>I did.</i> The memory came back in a rush. Smiler's screams had sounded almost human. His mane afire, he had reared up on his hind legs, blind with pain, lashing out with his hooves. <i>No, no. Not mine, he was not mine, <a href=\"/index.php/Reek#A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"Reek\">Reek</a> never had a horse.</i><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> and an <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> guard</cite></div>\n</blockquote> \n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smiler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_no